Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.39,0:23:00.02,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}A nervous breakdown
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.44,0:23:02.98,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You feel an urge inside, you crush
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.19,0:23:04.65,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}There's no escape now
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.28,0:23:07.82,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You try to change your life, you jump
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.90,0:23:09.57,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Another letdown
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.99,0:23:12.74,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}But then you hear a voice inside
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.74,0:23:14.37,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You gotta open up your vision
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.45,0:23:15.99,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}See the life bestowed on you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.08,0:23:18.20,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Blinded by reality
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.50,0:23:20.75,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Broken ideology
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.83,0:23:23.25,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Heart in captivity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.34,0:23:24.13,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hold on
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.21,0:23:25.42,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Exceeding the borders within
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.67,0:23:28.01,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Seize your capability
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.05,0:23:30.47,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Endless possibility
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.47,0:23:32.84,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Find your individuality
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.89,0:23:34.55,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Take pride, let the chase begin
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.68,0:23:38.02,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't tell me what direction you think I should take
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:39.48,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}『I know I'm gonna find the way』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.39,0:23:42.56,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't tell me that this sable is for my own sake
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.56,0:23:44.36,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}『Hear what I've got to say』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.27,0:23:47.32,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't tell me to believe the decisions you make
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.11,0:23:49.19,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}『I'm facing a new day』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.03,0:23:51.74,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}So open up your blinded eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.86,0:23:54.20,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Stop living a lie and start living your life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.45,0:23:56.33,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}My way or no way
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.74,0:23:59.04,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Today you're falling away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.37,0:24:00.91,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}My way or no way
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.54,0:24:03.96,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Today I'm breaking away
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.31,0:22:58.14,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,失汝心志　躯形难继
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.39,0:23:00.02,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,慌乱分崩离析
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.44,0:23:02.98,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,心潮涌动　冲荡破碎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.19,0:23:04.65,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,已是无路可退
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.28,0:23:07.82,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,逆天改命　奋力跃腾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.90,0:23:09.57,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,再落心灰意冷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.99,0:23:12.74,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,却闻心中轻语
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.74,0:23:14.37,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,放眼茫然四顾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.45,0:23:15.99,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,但见尘世夺予
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.08,0:23:18.20,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,现实毁盲双目
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.50,0:23:20.75,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,仅余碎裂思悟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.83,0:23:23.25,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,心亦牢牢禁锢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.34,0:23:24.13,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,勿言轻弃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.21,0:23:25.42,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,跨越心中束缚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.67,0:23:28.01,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,紧握汝力天成
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.05,0:23:30.47,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,迸发无尽可能
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.47,0:23:32.84,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,寻汝真我个性
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.89,0:23:34.55,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,昂首迈步前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.68,0:23:38.02,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,莫要擅自定吾前路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:39.48,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,『吾定将自寻通途』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.39,0:23:42.56,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,莫言黑暗皆为吾敌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.56,0:23:44.36,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,『但得静闻吾倾诉』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.27,0:23:47.32,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,莫诳吾从尔等好恶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.11,0:23:49.19,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,『吾自面崭新朝暮』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.03,0:23:51.74,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,故舍犹豫再开盲眼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.86,0:23:54.20,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,挣脱谎言自立世间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.45,0:23:56.33,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,足下再无别途
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.74,0:23:59.04,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,此时汝却飘然离去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.37,0:24:00.91,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,足下再无别途
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.54,0:24:03.96,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,今日吾将突破禁锢
